{"title":"Timer Online - Simple, Convenient and Free Timer","description":"Convenient, simple, accurate online timer with sound and completely free. You can open it in full screen or select the sound of the timer. Shows how much time is left before the timer expires.","content":"## Timer online\r\n\r\nA timer is a device that beeps after a certain amount of time.\r\n\r\nA timer is a very useful device that allows you to easily control your time. Nowadays, it makes no sense to buy a timer as a separate device, now it is right in the browser!\r\n\r\nAlso, do not confuse a timer with an alarm clock! The timer fires after a certain time and the response time depends on the time when the timer itself was set.\r\n\r\n## Online timer features\r\n\r\nThis timer has many useful features that you will definitely need:\r\n\r\n* Multiple timers can be set.\r\n* Allows you to set the time down to the second.\r\n* It is possible to change the sound signal or put your own.\r\n* You can watch the remaining time until the timer expires.\r\n* Displays the time when the timer was turned on.\r\n* The timer will remain on EVEN after closing the browser tab.\r\n* The timer is stored in memory, making it easy to reuse it.\r\n* Can work even without internet.\r\n\r\n\r\n## When is the Timer useful?\r\n\r\nIn some cases, you simply cannot do without a timer:\r\n\r\n1. Playing sports. Set a timer for the time that you want to devote yourself to training and do not be distracted by anything else. The timer will notify you when it's time to finish.\r\n2. During work. By setting a timer, you will always know when to take a break.\r\n3. Cooking. Time is the most important ingredient in cooking. The timer will help you follow the recipe exactly and will not allow the dish to be spoiled by the human factor.\r\n4. When spending time at the computer, you need to take small breaks. You can set a timer for half an hour to take a break after it goes off. This should have a positive effect on your health.\r\n\r\n## Arbitrary musical arrangement\r\n\r\nFor the timer, it is possible to set your own musical background for the alarm.\r\nTo do this, click on the `+` button next to the sound selection button. Next, upload the desired music, select it and apply the changes.\r\n\r\n\r\n## How to use\r\n\r\nOur timer is incredibly easy to use. You can take the time from the available list or choose your own. It's also a good idea to choose your own name for it if you plan to reuse it. A unique sound can be selected for each individual timer. After that, the timer is added to the panel on the right.\r\n\r\nAfter the specified time, the timer will work and play the selected signal.\r\n\r\nEach timer can be stopped and restarted if desired."}